DataElement.preferredName: Adjacency Matrix Mutual Information Value double One Dimensional Array
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A matrix with rows and columns labeled by graph vertices, with a 1 or 0 in position (vi,vj) according to whether vi and vj are adjacent or not._Expresses the extent to which the observed frequency of co-occurrence differs from that expected under the null hypothesis._A generic value domain for a one dimensional array containing double-precision 64 bit floating point values having a format of an integer mantissa followed by an optional 'E' or 'e' and an integer exponent.
